2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper discusses a new color quantization technique for image compression, which is a common problem in graphics. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image compression, which is a common problem in multimedia. 
4. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper discusses a technique for improving image compression for users with color vision deficiencies, which is relevant to human-computer interaction. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a large corpus of color vision acuity data obtained from a mobile game, which could potentially involve machine learning techniques.
